Description: Laboratory inventory management system
 Inventarium is a lightweight inventory management system designed
 for small laboratory teams who need a simple, fast, and reliable
 way to track consumables, reagents, and supplies.
 .
 Features:
  - Product hierarchy: Products, Packages, Batches, Labels
  - Barcode generation and scanning
  - Expiration tracking (FEFO management)
  - Reorder alerts
  - Multi-language support (Italian, English, Spanish)
